üöÄ Features
Sleek & Modern UI: Clean, minimalist design with a dark theme.

Fully Responsive: Looks great on all devices, from mobile phones to desktop screens.

Interactive Animations:

Dynamic particle background using tsParticles.

Engaging typing effect in the hero section.

Subtle on-scroll animations to reveal content.

Key Sections: Includes dedicated sections for About Me, Technical Skills, Projects, and an embedded Resume summary.

Easy Contact: A direct mailto: link in the contact section makes it easy for visitors to get in touch.

üõ†Ô∏è Technologies Used
This project was built using a simple and efficient tech stack:

HTML5: For the structure and content of the website.

Tailwind CSS: For all styling and creating a responsive layout without writing custom CSS.

JavaScript (ES6+): To power the interactive elements like the typing effect and the particle animation.

üîß How to Run Locally
To run this project on your local machine:

Clone the repository:

git clone [https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git](https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git)

Navigate to the project directory:

cd your-repo-name

Open the index.html file in your web browser. For the best experience, I recommend using the Live Server extension in Visual Studio Code.